This paper discusses the riskiness of spreadsheets and how to use control frameworks to reduce the dangers created by spreadsheets. It focuses on testing, which is a crucial element in spreadsheet controls. Therefore, it is most likely to belong to the categories of cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.SE (Software Engineering), cs.CY (Computers and Society), cs.GR (Graphics), and cs.PL (Programming Languages).
